{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.130\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">上行之诗。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">求助的祈祷</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.130.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>耶和华啊，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">我从深处求告你！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.130.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>主啊，求你听我的声音！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">求你侧耳听我恳求的声音！</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.130.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>耶和华啊，你若究察罪孽，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">主啊，谁能站得住呢？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.130.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>但在你有赦免之恩，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">要叫人敬畏你。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.130.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>我等候耶和华，我的心等候；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">我也仰望他的话。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.130.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>我的心等候主，胜于守夜的等候天亮，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">胜于守夜的等候天亮。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v7\"><sup id=\"Ps.130.7\" class=\"v7\">7</sup><span class=\"pn\">以色列</span>啊，你当仰望耶和华，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v7\">因耶和华有慈爱，有丰盛的救恩。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v8\"><sup id=\"Ps.130.8\" class=\"v8\">8</sup>他必救赎<span class=\"pn\">以色列</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v8\">脱离一切的罪孽。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}